Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:16.45,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What are these remnants of destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:20.08,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's a perfectly round opening,\Nlike someone pulled out a cork.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:22.23,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:25.96,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,The destruction continues on beyond this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:29.91,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,These are clearly signs that Avdol and \Nthe others encountered an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:34.39,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro! Break down this door! We're going in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:35.43,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:09.27,JoJo-MainTitle,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,2515)}JoJo's {\c&H2E0FB2&}Bizarre Adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:09.27,JoJo-MainTitle2,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(208,2515)}Stardust Crusaders
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:17.49,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Iggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:44.54,JoJo-EpTitle,epi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(458,632)}Episode 44  The Miasma of the Void, Cool Ice, Part 3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.87,0:02:52.76,JoJo-Location,blahlala,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,459)\b0\fs18}This story is fiction. The characters, groups, places, laws, and names \Nused in this program have no connection to any existing in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:04.50,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff. It is not by your hand that I bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:06.65,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,It is by Avdol's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:11.37,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:14.50,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I had planned to eradicate\Nboth you and Avdol all at once,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:16.92,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,but he knocked you out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:20.48,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, in such a situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:24.43,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,one would instinctively \Nfocus on protecting himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:27.85,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,This blood is the result of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.13,0:03:33.23,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,But although I am injured, \Nit will take some time until I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:36.66,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,I shall go finish off Joestar and the other two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:38.69,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,I will, without a doubt, eliminate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:47.28,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Iggy... I told you over and over \Nnot to use your Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.66,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to act all cool and shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.42,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I told you so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.75,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,Polnareff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:59.02,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Cool Ice said that a mere\Ndog could not have resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:01.27,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,That he could not possess a proud soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:04.76,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,But Stands are the soul's manifestation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:07.92,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Iggy's soul had moved on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:10.35,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It had no choice but to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:19.41,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This feeling in the sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:23.20,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,How could this have happened? Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.45,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It's an empty shell. A Stand's empty shell...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.75,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,This is cold annihilation...\NThe destruction of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:34.52,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I'm the one who survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.30,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Ig...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:42.46,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Iggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:50.35,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You're too slow, Cool Ice. \NAnd you're exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:53.51,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I have really bad luck when it comes to friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.51,0:04:56.94,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to save Iggy, \Nbut instead, he saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:14.37,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.47,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:21.02,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized how much I liked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:25.84,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It always happens this way.\NI only understand after they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.09,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were a stubborn, \Nshitty little mutt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.26,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,but I loved how you acted so stubborn,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.14,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,and refused to be friendly with any human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.96,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I realize now that your refusal to show
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:41.08,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,affection for anyone proved \Njust how proud you really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.25,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:49.57,JoJo-internal/narrator,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! It's because of your stubbornness that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.86,JoJo-Rumble,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H9C3946&}Rumble
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:13.14,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. Cool Ice, you bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:39.00,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:43.09,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You're immortal. DIO did \Nsomething to you, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:56.31,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What... i-is... this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:07:00.56,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't notice your body changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.74,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You received his blood, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:06.65,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you're becoming something\NI've heard stories about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:09.55,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as DIO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.85,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,A soulless, filthy vampire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.63,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.37,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you started to turn into a vampire
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.73,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,around the moment I stabbed \Nyou through the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.05,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:30.25,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indulge your obsession to the fullest! \NTry and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:32.64,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,You're obsessed with \Nprotecting DIO, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.39,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:38.47,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Cool Ice? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.73,JoJo-main,cool,0000,0000,0000,,You will not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.94,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Go to Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:34.86,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,A-Avdol... I-Iggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:43.93,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,W...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.26,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that an illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:49.30,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:58.80,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I have to climb up those stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.97,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and get to DIO.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:06.75,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to cry in sadness now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:18.20,JoJo-Avdol,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(426,518)}Avdol has died\NIggy has died
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.90,JoJo-Eyecatch3,signtop,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(709,1)}The Fool
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.91,JoJo-Eyecatch2,signbot,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(711,1)}Iggy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:28.83,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:33.46,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It has now been 43 days since \NJojo and the others departed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:35.67,JoJo-main,susie,0000,0000,0000,,Stop for a moment, Rosas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:37.68,JoJo-main,susie,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.80,Soba,whiteblack,0000,0000,0000,,Soba                   {\c&H462122&\fs24}Soba Midokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:45.12,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,Madam, you're not thinking about\Nstopping at that soba stand, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:46.13,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:48.12,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long since I've been in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:51.12,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have a bite \Nbefore I go see my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.12,0:09:53.86,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,You hold my little turtle for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:57.07,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't, Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.70,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,These places are intended for busy men,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.77,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,not for ladies like yourself. \NThat is the Japanese way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:05.20,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,You are Madam Joestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:08.92,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hush. I'm going to record \Na commemorative video.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.36,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Very good! Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:11.75,Soba 2,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Soba
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.36,0:10:14.25,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,This plebeian atmosphere... It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:16.17,Do Not,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Do not puke or piss
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:20.48,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Rosas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:25.68,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Have you not told her about \Nher daughter Holly's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:31.46,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up, Rosas! Come, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.44,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll be right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:40.47,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,I... I haven't told her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.72,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,She came to Japan thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:45.47,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,she was just visiting her daughter,\Nwho had mild pneumonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:49.66,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,I have served the Joestar family for 30 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:53.88,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,ever since Miss Holly was in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:57.68,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,I know I should have told her the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:00.33,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,But... I lacked the courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:03.97,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,So we arrived in Japan before I could tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:06.94,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Holly's strength has run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:09.37,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,She has only a few days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.44,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell her, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:18.85,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,N-No... I have lied this long \Nto Madam about Miss Holly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:21.74,Part-Timers,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Hiring\NPart-timers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:21.74,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:26.08,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that she might be cured if
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.23,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the man called DIO is defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:31.75,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. {\i1}If{\i0} he is defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:37.37,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Holly's body is reacting \Nto an energy called a Stand,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:41.36,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,which only certain people can see, \Nand is being overwhelmed by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:44.42,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,By the evil energy of the man known as DIO...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:47.51,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,The Madam cannot see Stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:51.73,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But when she encounters the \Nshadow of death, she will sense it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:55.06,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,You must go tell Madam Joestar right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.49,0:11:57.22,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shadow of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.82,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Rosas! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.96,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,You should have some curry udon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:10.25,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,Madam, there's something I must tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:13.08,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I must get some footage of the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:15.96,Family Planning,red,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1500,1)}Family\NPlanning
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:15.96,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,vending machine serving that \Npeculiar energy drink, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.96,Skin,signblue,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}Premium Skin
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:19.53,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Very good. Would you like one, Rosas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:24.05,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,Madam, please stop! Those are not drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.64,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please listen, Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:28.47,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? To what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.68,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The truth is, Miss Holly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.51,0:12:36.33,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,This Japanese person is so unique and cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:37.65,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:41.44,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, hello, give me smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.44,JoJo-main,yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:46.20,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission to videotape me, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.24,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:49.08,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam, please get back in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.41,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.87,JoJo-main,yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here, damn it! \NAre you messing with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.54,JoJo-main,yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over that camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:59.01,JoJo-main,yaku,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell do you think you are,\Nyou foreign granny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:02.17,JoJo-main,yakuza,0000,0000,0000,,Want to see some blood, \Nyou shitty old woman? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.28,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's quite enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:07.09,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not lay a finger on the Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:08.72,JoJo-Kabam,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Kabam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:13.99,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,Madam, please! Learn a bit more about Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:15.31,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:20.38,JoJo-internal/narrator,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,I-I couldn't tell her
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:23.90,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,that Miss Holly only has a few days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:27.07,JoJo-internal/narrator,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear seeing Madam in shock and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:44.93,JoJo-internal/narrator,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,We've come this far before I could tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:48.36,JoJo-internal/narrator,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,The Kujo household is almost in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.16,JoJo-internal/narrator,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,I must tell her now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.74,JoJo-internal/narrator,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,I must be the one to tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:57.99,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Rosas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:00.27,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know there's something you want to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:05.60,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,I already know what's been troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.68,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,My daughter's life is in danger, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:22.20,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,When I called her from New York,\NHolly always sounded cheerful and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:26.01,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,She said that she just had a little cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.76,0:14:28.89,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph would also call me\Nwhile he was on the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:33.01,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,saying that he was doing fine \Nand oh so terribly busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:37.01,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,But somehow I knew
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:41.56,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,that something terrible was happening \Nto my daughter and my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:45.12,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,I've lived with my husband for fifty years,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:47.65,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,and I gave birth to my daughter, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:51.35,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,I was frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:53.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was too scared to verify the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:56.84,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,The more I wanted to see my daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:59.53,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the more frightened I was to come to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:04.36,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're discussing it now,\Nwe should tell you clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:07.54,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Holly's survival will depend \Nupon these next few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:10.34,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar and the others \Nwent to Egypt to address
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.03,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the source of her illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.76,JoJo-main,person,0000,0000,0000,,but I have not heard any news from them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:19.19,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please forgive me for not telling you, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:23.70,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,There was nothing we could do for Miss Holly,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:25.94,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and that was so painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.67,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,It was so cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:32.11,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,What nonsense are you speaking, Rosas?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.91,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,There is just one thing we can do for Holly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.26,0:16:01.06,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Holly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:12.15,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.99,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Rosas, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.23,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,The one thing we can do for my daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:20.13,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,is believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:25.38,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know the details, but I have faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.94,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,If my Joseph and my grandson, Jotaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:31.58,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,are trying to do something to save my daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:33.46,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,then I will believe in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:37.78,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I met that man\Nin Italy fifty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:41.48,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,he has never betrayed my expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:44.14,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Once he decides he's going to do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.40,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,he will follow through, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:50.33,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in Jotaro and Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:54.78,JoJo-main,suzie,0000,0000,0000,,Get better, and we'll all be \Ntogether as a family again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:57.25,JoJo-main,holy,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:03.91,JoJo-main,rosas,0000,0000,0000,,Madam... Miss Holly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:12.84,JoJo-Eyecatch3,signtop,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(818,1)}Star Platinum
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.84,JoJo-Eyecatch2,signbot,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(882,1)}Jotaro Kujo
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.56,0:17:22.81,JoJo-main,nukesaku,0000,0000,0000,,Cool Ice... Billie Jean... D'Arby Younger...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:26.69,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,All of you were fools after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:27.98,JoJo-Bam,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Bam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:40.24,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but belly laugh in sheer satisfaction \Nto think they got what they deserved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.41,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,Calling me "Nukesaku" like I'm some moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:47.54,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're the dumbasses who got killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:50.91,JoJo-flashback,cool,0000,0000,0000,,Nukesaku, it is impossible for you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:53.13,JoJo-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,to defeat Joestar and the \Nothers with your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.92,JoJo-flashback,ter,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:58.59,JoJo-flashback,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... Let me in on the action, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:01.35,JoJo-flashback,cool,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing more than a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:05.10,JoJo-flashback,kenny,0000,0000,0000,,Just try and interfere. We'll kill you if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:08.11,JoJo-flashback,ter,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay put, Nukesaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:14.28,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one who finishes off Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.20,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! There's something in \Nfront of us, to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:34.59,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:38.05,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:42.85,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink my blood! \NPlease don't drink my blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:48.72,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever you say! \NSo please, spare my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:53.46,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, just wait a second. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:57.73,JoJo-main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,I won't try to run away again! \NSo please... spare my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.73,0:18:59.05,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:02.49,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't DIO's minions, and we aren't vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.72,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You can consider us friends. \NWe'll help you, so calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:08.00,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:13.37,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends? A-Are you really friends, not foes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:15.75,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Will you really help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:18.16,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We're friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:21.34,JoJo-Grar,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Crush
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:26.18,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Of justice, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:31.21,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:34.18,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help you go straight to Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.39,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kakyoin?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:44.45,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible! Wh-Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.17,0:19:47.18,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,How did you figure it out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.71,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,My power is invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:53.78,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Is your power having the face of a \Nwoman on the back of your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:57.38,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You should have at least \Nturned your hands around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.43,0:20:02.85,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.56,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize... Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.39,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nukesaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.97,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Where's DIO's room? Tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:13.90,JoJo-main,kakyo,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro, don't knock him out. \NLet's have him guide us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:16.57,JoJo-main,nuike,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:22.15,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,You called me "Nukesaku"... \NDon't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.43,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:29.16,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am immortal, for the blood \Nof Lord DIO is in my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:36.12,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did you just say you were immortal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:38.74,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a vampire like DIO...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:44.05,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, I guess I'll have to \Nsee just how immortal you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.10,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.32,0:21:02.09,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you are immortal. \NBut even if you are a vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.79,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,it's still possible to cut you into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.79,0:21:09.01,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Lead us to DIO. The sun's setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:13.34,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... But may I ask you one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:17.92,JoJo-main,nuke,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that they call me "Nukesaku"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:20.92,JoJo-main,jojo,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.76,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Those curtains were made of some nice cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:10.24,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can move better, and even jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.60,0:23:11.88,JoJo-main,jean,0000,0000,0000,,It still hurts,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.88,0:23:14.56,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't have time to \Nlose heart or worry about pain.
